---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import "@fontsource/inter/400.css";
import "@fontsource/inter/600.css";
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How this site collects, uses, and protects personal data."
  themeColor="#111111"
  bodyClass="legal"
>
  <main id="main" class="legal-wrap">
    <a class="back" href="/">&larr; Back</a>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: placeholder — set this to your real launch date.</p>

    <p class="note">
      <strong>Template note:</strong> this page is placeholder legal copy shipped
      with the design template. Replace every bracketed item with your real
      business details, and have the final text reviewed by a lawyer for the
      regions you actually serve (GDPR/UK GDPR, CCPA/CPRA, LGPD, PIPEDA, etc.)
      before publishing.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Who we are</h2>
    <p>[Business name], [registered address], is the data controller for this
    website. Contact us at [privacy@yourdomain.com] with any question about
    this policy or your data.</p>

    <h2>2. What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Information you submit through contact or booking forms (name, email, message).</li>
      <li>Basic technical data (browser type, device, approximate location from IP) via optional analytics — only after you accept optional cookies.</li>
      <li>No payment data is stored on this site; payments are processed by a third-party provider under its own policy.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Why we process it</h2>
    <p>To respond to enquiries, operate and improve the site, meet legal
    obligations, and — only with consent — measure site usage.</p>

    <h2>4. Legal basis (EEA/UK visitors)</h2>
    <p>Consent (Art. 6(1)(a) GDPR) for optional cookies and marketing;
    legitimate interest (Art. 6(1)(f)) for essential site operation and
    security; contract (Art. 6(1)(b)) where you request a service.</p>

    <h2>5. Your rights</h2>
    <p>Depending on your location you may have the right to access, correct,
    delete, or export your data, to withdraw consent at any time, and to
    object to processing. EEA/UK residents may lodge a complaint with their
    local supervisory authority. California residents have rights under the
    CCPA/CPRA, including the right to opt out of the "sale" or "sharing" of
    personal information — this site does not sell personal information.</p>

    <h2>6. Retention</h2>
    <p>We keep enquiry data only as long as needed to respond and meet legal
    obligations, then delete or anonymise it.</p>

    <h2>7. Third parties</h2>
    <p>We only share data with processors strictly needed to run the site
    (e.g. hosting, email delivery, optional analytics), each bound by a data
    processing agreement.</p>

    <h2>8. International transfers</h2>
    <p>Where data is transferred outside your region, we rely on appropriate
    safeguards such as Standard Contractual Clauses.</p>

    <h2>9. Changes</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy; the date above reflects the latest revision.</p>

    <nav class="legal-links" aria-label="Legal pages">
      <a href="/cookies">Cookie Policy</a>
      <a href="/accessibility">Accessibility Statement</a>
    </nav>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-wrap {
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin-inline: auto;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 6rem;
    font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
    color: #1c1c1c;
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  .back {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: #555;
  }
  h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .updated { color: #666; font-size: 0.875rem; margin-bottom: 1.75rem; }
  .note {
    background: #f3f3f1;
    border-radius: 0.6rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 2.25rem;
  }
  h2 { font-size: 1.15rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; }
  p, li { font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
  ul { padding-inline-start: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-links {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #e6e6e3;
    padding-top: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  .legal-links a { text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
